{"tid":548333,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[清新甜美] 四年燒酒代言 超李英愛金泰熙 IU成最長壽模特","createTime":"2018-02-02T12:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T01:43:45.000Z","uid":34643,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8831e79245d6ee030a31f8edc3518f1270c89244","tid":548333,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/0069TCxOly1fnzzwkps41j30u00u00wu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F0069TCxOly1fnzzwkps41j30u00u00wu.jpg&h=b80eb9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2日，SBS新聞報道&ldquo;歌手IU升級為其代言的燒酒公司簽約的最長壽模特。IU於2014年底簽約該燒酒公司，首次代言燒酒，今年IU繼續代言，成為了該公司連續四年簽約的最長壽的燒酒模特。此前，該公司曾簽過李英愛，金泰熙，文彩媛等明星。IU開始代言後，有人評價其清新的形像和品牌燒酒干淨的味道相得益彰。公司相關人士也表示IU在打造品牌正面積極的形像上起到了很大的作用，為了表示感謝還給最長壽模特IU准備了名譽社員證。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gslb.miaopai.com/stream/X4hcWPE49WzoYOVwRBIhAQpSIOZsW3gfBi1fNQ__.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgslb.miaopai.com%2Fstream%2FX4hcWPE49WzoYOVwRBIhAQpSIOZsW3gfBi1fNQ__.mp4&d=E%2Ff4k2MHme2j1VCQJ%2FdWsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c89bf79a\" target=\"_blank\">http://gslb.miaopai.com/stream/X4hcWPE49WzoYOVwRBIhAQpSIOZsW3gfBi1fNQ__.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"2f5c31af2d94ffd3d685d083895e3923d202508c","tid":548333,"uid":65144,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母拎iu呢隻雞同李英愛比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4d097336f765d5edba4c0943600c8bb4fa34c0","tid":548333,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T17:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/be3ff1c4gy1fo2ib3s22zj22lj2fv1f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2Fbe3ff1c4gy1fo2ib3s22zj22lj2fv1f3.jpg&h=ae8c075f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/be3ff1c4gy1fo2ib4hr3wj20ku0jh79v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k